name: Umibozu
skill: Deals 2367/2827 DMG to 3 enemies (melee priority). Decreases targets' speed by 30/36% for a limited time.
ability: Skill attacks by Phantasma team members have a slight chance of inflicting Stun.

additional_data.description: A spirit who controls a black giant that sinks ships at night. The giant does whatever he tells it to do, so if sailors are noisy at night when he's trying to sleep, he summons his giant to silence them. He pretty much just lets it run wild on the open seas until the noise goes away.

main: "I'll destroy anyone who causes a ruckus on the open seas."
skill: "You won't like me when I'm angry."
summon: "I'll shut up those small fries once and for all."
limit_break: "I think my giant just got a little gianter."
